column5: I took a walk out yesterday to look for some . But I didn't see any yet. Took a ride from to westt end of the city to East and back. I noticed Mimico is under construction.  Looks good so far. Still a lot of work. And they have everything blocked off. Should be interesting. I see some good coming out of this.     dsn

Looks like they are going to build a causeway and a bridge to a spot that the road already goes to. How is it anything but a waste of tax dollars?  This isn't another McGuinty enerygy saving ploicy is it?
I tried fishing that area from shore for pike... no luck and im not going back there. But if ur into carp i saw some big ones. Although in spring theyre all along the shoreline of lake o
